OL,3,CBBC News ratings: something to brag
OL,4,Cabout
OL,6,FSome recent ratings should destroy the
OL,7,Fmyths that the corporation is somehow
OL,8,Firrelevant in this age of unlimited
OL,9,Fchoice and that linear TV itself is
OL,10,Fdead.
OL,12,FOn Friday night, The Traitors won 5.5m
OL,13,Fviewers. All three episodes this week
OL,14,Fscored above 5m in the overnights.
OL,16,FOn some days last week, BBC One and
OL,17,FTwo had a combined all day audience
OL,18,Fshare of around 33pc.
OL,20,FThat is remarkable in this day and age.
