OL,3,CBBC News ratings: something to brag
OL,4,Cabout
OL,6,FSo too are the ratings for some news
OL,7,Fprogrammes.
OL,9,FOn Wednesday, the regional news
OL,10,Fprogrammes at 6.30pm got a collective
OL,11,Frating of 4.9m.
OL,13,FHelped by the cold weather, the main
OL,14,Fpart of the BBC News at One was
OL,15,Fgetting up to 2.5m. The News at Six
OL,16,Fwas comfortably above 4m.
