OL,3,CBBC News ratings: something to brag
OL,4,Cabout
OL,6,FThese programmes have a healthy lead
OL,7,Fover their direct rivals on ITV 1. But
OL,8,Fmuch more importantly, they are the
OL,9,Fkind of figures those who claim the
OL,10,Fmainstream media is just a legacy can
OL,11,Fonly dream of.
OL,13,FThe BBC must make sure these figures
OL,14,Fare known about widely.
OL,16,FThey are not only a crucial part of
OL,17,Fthe case to justify its own continuing
OL,18,Fexistence, they are also an important
OL,19,Fpart of the wider defence of the
OL,20,Fmainstream media against those who
OL,21,Fwant to see it weakened or destroyed.
