OL,3,CBBC News ratings: something to brag
OL,4,Cabout
OL,6,FIt is worth questioning the motivation
OL,7,Fof some of those critics.
OL,9,FThere is one other rating last week
OL,10,Fwhich is worth mentioning for entirely
OL,11,Fdifferent reasons.
OL,13,FThe film Where Eagles Dare has been
OL,14,Fshown countless times over the decades
OL,15,Fon major and minor channels. I think I
OL,16,Fstill have a VHS recording of a
OL,17,Fscreening on BBC One in the mid-
OL,18,Feighties.
OL,20,FLast Sunday afternoon, it got around
OL,21,F1m viewers on BBC Two.
