OL,3,CBBC News ratings: something to brag
OL,4,Cabout
OL,6,FYes, an old film on a major channel
OL,7,Fcan beat much-publicised shows on
OL,8,Fstreaming services and minor channels
OL,9,Fby a country mile.
OL,11,FIt's a good yarn but hardly
OL,12,Fhistorically accurate. There were no
OL,13,FNazi helicopters. That is the kind of
OL,14,Fnonsense you'll find today in
OL,15,Fpoisonous corners of cyberspace rather
OL,16,Fthan harmless, but brilliantly made,
OL,17,Fhokum.
OL,19,FAnd the idea that linear TV and big
OL,20,Fchannels are dead or a mere legacy is
OL,21,Fequally fantastic
