OL,3,CBBC News ratings: something to brag
OL,4,Cabout
OL,6,FThere is no point longing for the days
OL,7,Fwhen unremarkable sitcoms would get
OL,8,F10m viewers. Viewers only had three
OL,9,Fchannels to choose from and video
OL,10,Frecorders were a novelty.
OL,12,FBut good programmes on major channels
OL,13,Fstill have a power which minor
OL,14,Fchannels and streaming services can
OL,15,Frarely come close to.
OL,17,FThe BBC needs to make sure this fact
OL,18,Fis understood ` by the wider public,
OL,19,Fby politicians and journalists.
